@node "Einstellungen" "Etiketti 2.60 - Printer configuration"

 @{u}Printer configuration@{uu}

 The @{"window" alink "EtikettiPrefs.ilbm/main" 0} for the printer configuartion is
 structured in three groups.

 @{u}Group rows@{uu}

 In this group you can choose the number and the position of
 label lines.


 @{u}Group columns@{uu}

 In this group you can choose the number and the position of
 label columns.


 @{u}Group save - use - cancel@{uu}

 With this buttons you can save, use or reject your new
 settings.
@endnode

